  h2 Alert with no content
  p An alert message can be created with no content wrapper leaving only the title. The same classes #{inline_code(".alert-message")}, #{inline_code(".alert-warning")}, #{inline_code(".alert-error")}, or #{inline_code(".alert-success")} to display the correct color and icon for the alert.
  p Because of the modular style of the alert module the core markup can be adjusted to be semantically correct without creating the need to create new CSS.

