  h2 Inline Alert
  p An inline alert message can be created from any HTML element as long as the correct class is attached. The classes #{inline_code(".alert-inline-message")}, #{inline_code(".alert-inline-warning")}, #{inline_code(".alert-inline-error")}, or #{inline_code(".alert-inline-success")} can be used to display the correct color and icon for the alert.
  p The content should be a single sentence or a short paragraph.

